.TH LOOTSHEET-ENTRY-CUSTOM 1 "Mar 2026" "LootSheet" "LootSheet Manual"
.SH NAME
lootsheet-entry-custom \\- Record a guided custom journal entry
.SH SYNOPSIS
lootsheet entry custom [flags]
.SH DESCRIPTION
LootSheet CLI

Usage:
  lootsheet entry custom --description TEXT [--date YYYY-MM-DD] --debit CODE:AMOUNT[:MEMO] --credit CODE:AMOUNT[:MEMO]

Defaults:
  --date  today

Amounts accept D&D 5e denominations: PP, GP, EP, SP, CP (case insensitive).

Examples:
  lootsheet entry custom --description "Gear transfer" --debit 1300:5GP --credit 1000:5GP
  lootsheet entry custom --description "Split payout" --debit 1000:10GP --credit 4000:8GP --credit 4100:2GP
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
--credit=stringArray
credit line in CODE:AMOUNT[:MEMO] format (default: [])
.TP
--date=string
entry date in YYYY-MM-DD (defaults to today) (default: )
.TP
--debit=stringArray
debit line in CODE:AMOUNT[:MEMO] format (default: [])
.TP
--description=string
journal entry description (required) (default: )
.TP
-h, --help
help for custom
.SH SEE ALSO
lootsheet-entry(1)
